ExternalParameters
public class SlowQueryWithInputDatastoreParameters<T,​I>
extends SlowQueryDatastoreParameters<T>
The input parameters required to report a slow datastore query on the TracedMethod including a correlating input query. Do not use this class directly. Instead use DatastoreParameters.
Since:
3.36.0
